<plot>This experimental movie features the insane beauty cult of our modern society and its causes. The story is going back to Grimm's tales and further. The story read by the big sister turns into a feminist statement about not exactly fitting "into the shoe". Cinderella has to go through several stages of her nightmare until she goes insane herself and breaks down. In the end it is the question what beauty cult might do to the little girl in the future.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?014068</url></doc>
